Author: Mathias Uhlenbrock
Headline: Astronomical Database v0.2 beta released
Content_Right:
Astronomical Database v0.2 beta is released for public testing. The database has been updated to reflect recent changes in the following software packages:
  • PostgreSQL 12.1

Author: Mathias Uhlenbrock
Headline: Astronomical Database v0.2 alpha released
Content_Right:
Astronomical Database v0.2 alpha is released for public testing. The database has been updated to reflect recent changes in the following software packages:
  • Django 2.2
  • PostgreSQL 11.4

Author: Mathias Uhlenbrock
Headline: Astronomical Database v0.1 beta released
Content_Right:
Astronomical Database v0.1 beta is released for public testing.
  • Links are more pronounced now
  • Changed symbol for stars with unknown radii
  • Changed symbol for gas planets
  • New catalogue 'Other stars' for stars which could not be sorted otherwise
Bugfixes
  • Fixed template code not concordant with HTML5 standard
